    <div class="container-fluid background" id="history">
            <h1>Our history</h1>
            <p>Since 1924 Toy Tanks been delivering the very best in tank warfare.</p>
            <p>Our tank products and services operate across a wide variety of countries. Our business is underpinned by a deep understanding of technology, engineering and specialist tank warfare. Our first tank, the P121, first went into service in 1939 and since then we have continually innovated and improved on tank design and functionality to deliver on our customers needs.</p>
            <P>Information on our tanks can be found below along with the tank configurator to calculate the cost of your required tank.</p>
            <br>
            <p>Camouflage can be added to all of our tanks at a cost of £200,000</p>
