                <p class="card-text">The T01 Destroyer can operate in a wide variety of environments. It features the latest P122 cannon with an automated fire and explosion compression system. It has a top speed of 75mph and a single machine gun. Built with versatility in mind it's rugged track design gives it both speed and mobility over any terrain it may encounter.</p>
