            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">C23 Laserquest</h5>
                <p class="card-text">The Laserquest is the tank for the future containing the very latest technology and state of the art materials. It's stealth mirror technology enables it to evade enemy radar and infrared detection systems with an estimated top speed of around 60mph. The armament includes as 125mm laser cannon. A remote controlled turret operates the cannon and autopilot system allows the tank to be operated without a driver.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Price: £6.5m</li>
                    <li>Top speed: 60mph</li>
                    <li>Range: 420 miles</li>
